---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — Seglectic Systems"
  description="Seglectic Systems is a dark, experimental R&D studio building tools and systems at the edge of software and hardware."
>
  <div class="about-wrap">
    <header class="about-header">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1 class="title">Seglectic Systems</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        Seglectic Systems is a dark, experimental R&D studio. The work here lives at the intersection
        of software, hardware, and embedded systems — built to explore, to understand, and occasionally
        to ship.
      </p>
      <p>
        Projects range from computer vision tools running on Raspberry Pi to experimental terminal
        emulators written in Rust. The common thread is curiosity: what happens when you go low-level,
        when you instrument the physical world, when you build the thing you wish existed.
      </p>
      <p>
        Nothing here is polished for mass consumption. These are tools and systems in motion —
        some active, some in prototype, some shelved. The devlog tracks what's happening and why.
      </p>
      <p>
        All work is open source where possible.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="links">
      <a href="https://github.com/Seglectic" class="link-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        GitHub
      </a>
      <a href="/projects" class="link-btn">
        Projects
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-wrap {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .about-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm) 0;
  }

  .title {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .prose {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .prose p {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-md) 0;
  }

  .prose p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .links {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .link-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, color 0.15s;
  }

  .link-btn:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: var(--accent);
  }
</style>
